Package: LotekFilter
Title: Filter and Process Raw Lotek JSATS Files
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Derrick", "Alcott", , "derrick.alcott@wildlife.ca.gov", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Processes, reformats, and removes false-positive detections from Lotek (or other) JSATS acoustic telemetry receivers. Designed to process multiple files in parallel using multiple CPU cores to increase processing efficiency.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 3.6.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
